We noticed something on your product page
==========================================

Hi there,

Prowl detected <%= @issues.length == 1 ? "a potential issue" : "#{@issues.length} potential issues" %> on "<%= @product_page.title %>" that may affect your customers' ability to purchase.

<% @issues.each_with_index do |issue, i| %>
Issue <%= i + 1 %>: <%= issue.title %>
<%= "-" * 60 %>
<%= issue.merchant_explanation %>
<% if issue.merchant_suggested_fix.present? %>

Suggested fix:
<%= issue.merchant_suggested_fix %>
<% end %>
<% if issue.ai_confirmed == true && issue.ai_confidence.present? %>
🤖 AI confirmed this issue with <%= (issue.ai_confidence * 100).round %>% confidence.
<% end %>

Stop alerts for this issue: <%= @acknowledge_urls[issue.id] %>

<% end %>
We recommend reviewing the page to ensure customers can complete their purchase.

View page details: <%= @app_url %>

---
We only alert you when we're confident there's a real issue. This helps us avoid false alarms.
